title: Starlink satellites lift off on SpaceX Falcon 9 from Cape Canaveral (video)
description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 carrying 29 Starlink satellites launched from the Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Florida on Wednesday, Jan. 14, 2026.
